M_SCT[1319]='405. ‘When rebirth ceases, old age and death cease.’ That’s what I said. Is that how you see this or not?”';
M_SCT[1320]='“That’s how we see it.”';
M_SCT[1321]='‘When continued existence ceases, rebirth ceases.’ …';
M_SCT[1322]='‘When ignorance ceases, choices cease.’ That’s what I said. Is that how you see this or not?”';
M_SCT[1323]='“That’s how we see it.”';
